  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/3144945-alex">Alex</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer15201445976637825589"><i>Steven wrote: &quot;Don&apos;t you think it is possible that there was no authorial intent in some of Wyndham&apos;s decisions but that he simply let the story unfol</i></span>
  <span id="freeText15201445976637825589" style="display:none"><i>Steven wrote: "Don't you think it is possible that there was no authorial intent in some of Wyndham's decisions but that he simply let the story unfold in a way that would lead to the most exciting conflicts?"</i><br /><br />I feel confident that it this isn't it. There's so <i>much</i> philosophizing in this book! I mean, they're constantly making speeches! No, I don't think it's possible to read this book with any real attention and think its messaging is an accident.</span>
