<span id="freeTextContainer15963224063697504185">A book everyone should read. I love it when a story takes a jab at humanity and how balls up it generally is or can get. <br/><br/>A rather amusing, cleanly told story. Amongst the many, many, many (oh so many) crappy post apocalyptic books out there, this still has to be one of the best and most original. It has walking killer plants for goodness sakes!! <br/><br/>Read it, and you&apos;ll never look at your garden in the same way again...<br/><br/>Very cleanly written, short and interesting.</span>
