<span id="freeTextContainer12402580156628328776">Really enjoyed this post-apocalyptic tale which I wasn&apos;t expecting to like so much. It didn&apos;t really sound as dated as some other books of the time and was quite humorous in places. What a great opening line too!</span>
  <span id="freeText12402580156628328776" style="display:none">Really enjoyed this post-apocalyptic tale which I wasn't expecting to like so much. It didn't really sound as dated as some other books of the time and was quite humorous in places. What a great opening line too!</span>
